  "description": "Use when configuring or troubleshooting the B2B/B2C Commerce product catalog \u2014 ProductCatalog, ProductCategory, ProductCategoryProduct, WebStoreCatalog, CommerceEntitlementPolicy, product attributes, and product variants. Trigger keywords: product catalog, product category, commerce catalog, entitlement policy, product variants, product attributes, catalog visibility. NOT for CPQ product catalog (bundles, options, price rules) or for loading standard Product2/Pricebook2 data outside Commerce.",
  "file_location": "skills/admin/commerce-product-catalog",
  "id": "admin/commerce-product-catalog",
  "inputs": [
    "B2B or B2C Commerce store name and WebStore record Id",
    "ProductCatalog Id(s) currently associated to the store via WebStoreCatalog",
    "List of ProductCategory records and their hierarchy",
    "CommerceEntitlementPolicy name(s) and associated BuyerGroup(s)",
    "Product2 records with their attribute set configuration (for variants)",
    "Whether the store uses search indexing (Salesforce Search or Einstein Search)"
